    "Our findings affirmed that majority of the top cited papers are conference papers and are at least 9 years old.",
    "The co-occurrence analysis evidenced literature review analysis, data source (social media, questionnaire, and electronic health records), sentiment analysis and public health (diabetes, COVID-19, vaccine, schizophrenia, and depression) as the core emerging themes; Whilst our TM approach indicates that the application of TM for aspect-based sentiment analysis, event detection, image segmentation and classification are sparsely studied.",
    "Lastly, our analysis identified the future research direction of TM application as medical record analysis, public health & social media, information mining and literature review synthesis.",
